{"lemma":"قَهْقَرَى","slug":"قَهْقَرَى","root":"ق.ه.ق.ر","root_slug":"ق-ه-ق-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ه-ق-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36334"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D9%87%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36334","headword_ar":"قَهْقَرَى","root":"qhqr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A returning backwards;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a retiring, going backwards, without turning the face towards the direction in which one goes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) the dual is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qahoqaraAni","text_ar":"قَهْقَرَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAmb, K;) like as the dual of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawozalaY","text_ar":"خَوْزَلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawozalaAni","text_ar":"خَوْزَلَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) because this letter is deemed difficult to pronounce with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the dual. (TA.) When you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajaEotu AlqahoqaraY","text_ar":"رَجَعْتُ القَهْقَرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I returned backwards;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], it is as though you said I returned with the returning which is known by this name; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqhqrY","text_ar":"القهقرى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a mode of returning. (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aY AlqahoqaraY","text_ar":"مَشَى القَهْقَرَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He reverted from the state in which he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the course which he was following; revolted; apostatized."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, from a trad.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}